author: Daniel Brettig
title: Cricket Australia contracts delayed by coronavirus planning
description: Contingency planning to prepare for the possibility of a severely affected home summer also affecting state and BBL contracts | ESPNcricinfo.com
content:
Contingency planning to prepare for the possibility of a severely affected home summer has forced a delay in the release of Cricket Australia's annual contracts for men and women, with state and Big Bash League contracts also uncertain.
